Description.SourceString: Many attacks and skills can create elemental terrain. Levels can also be filled with traps that create terrain. Traps follow the pattern of their element - Water streams through the level like a river, Fire erupts randomly, and Nature grows in all directions from its central location, Dark slithers in a snake-like pattern, and Light bursts in a cross-like pattern.
